Rowdy Wolf:





Rowdy Wolf held back a laugh from KitKat's question. It seemed to be the 
main thing he had to explain. "I don't know where I came from." he replied. 
"All I can remember is coming on-line to a barren place. I traveled until I 
found somewhere I could make a home of. I was alone. I stayed that way for a 
long time, until I found Quickstrike in my territory." He wasn't sure if he 
should tell her he attacked him. "He told me about the Predacons. I agreed 
to stay in my territory until he needed me. Now, I guess he needs me." He 
shook his head while in motion. "Tell me, how did Quickstrike become second 
in command?"
